        "created_at": "2023-11-25T21:51:12.964Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=4836968&amp;iNote=10813955\"><b>1969 Louis Jadot Volnay</b></a> - France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Volnay (11/25/2023)<br>\nHighly perfumed, with aromas of decaying rose, spruce, freshly tilled earth and ripe strawberry. The palate is silky and possesses a core of sweet fruit. There's plenty of savoury nuance and a line of fine, minerally acidity. It builds and fans out and is persistent. A wonderful showing from a relatively humble bottle.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></p>",
